data.description: A gorgeous split foyer single family home with 4 bedrooms and 3 full baths.  3 spacious bedrooms and 2 full baths on the main level, and 1 bedroom and 1 full bath in the basement.  The home boasts a huge living room, a dining room with natural lighting, a kitchen with ample amount of storage, and an eat-in kitchen.  A rear deck and huge backyard, great for entertaining family and friends.  MAKE IT YOURS!  Schedule a showing today!
